{"tid":974677,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★World No Win7] 微軟唱衰Win7的各種論調今年年底就會蜂擁而至","createTime":"2019-01-09T05:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T12:11:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a784857aaf455717c05ca1be2c64cdde5a2c9152","tid":974677,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:17:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Windows 7將在2020年停止支持：微軟巴不得趕緊停止</span><br />\n<br />\nWindows 7將在2020年1月正式停止支持，但最近，微軟似乎正在和它的合作夥伴合作，巴不得讓每個人都知道Windows 7將停止支持，然後敦促用戶趕緊升級到Windows 10。<br />\n<br />\n根據統計，目前Windows 7市場份額達到43%，微軟相關負責人已經敦促渠道合作夥伴，想辦法讓用戶意識到Windows 7的生命週期即將結束，升級到更為安全的Windows 10系統十分必要。<br />\n<br />\n作為Windows 10增長重要的窗口期，如何讓這些用戶不轉向其他的系統是一門大學問，微軟相關負責人表示，如果能利用好這個機會，將會為微軟帶來高達1000億美元的商業價值。<br />\n<br />\n預計<span style=\"color: red;\">微軟唱衰Windows 7的各種論調今年年底就會蜂擁而至</span>，到時候應該會迎來一波Windows 10升級高峰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com/html/win7/372286.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com%2Fhtml%2Fwin7%2F372286.htm&d=FIkHPYVvt3hp7fUlEaYO6MP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=744fcc28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com/html/win7/372286.htm</a>"},{"pid":"608c8ba01a064fead544c411d3d19473564586f1","tid":974677,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401c76a4ca91234ef4f14ceea76b2381eadaf7b5","tid":974677,"uid":71913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:27:46.000Z","msg":"應該出7.1<br />\n<br />\n繼續更新win7<br />\n<br />\n而唔係繼續整廢window"},{"pid":"fc0e880b